
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .button { background: #3b82f6; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to ProfitWise AI!</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining ProfitWise AI. We're excited to help you on your investment journey!</p>
    <p>Get started by:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Setting up your portfolio</li>
      <li>Exploring AI insights</li>
      <li>Connecting with other traders</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">Visit Your Dashboard</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
